{
  "texts": [
    "The system is based on open source code, enabling the community to reproduce and build on it.",
    "We release the code for our pipeline, prompting workflow and Web application.",
    "The retrieval indexes, including the new full text search index, are available as Semantic Scholar APIs and dataset downloads, and are continually updated with new articles (Kinney et al., 2023).",
    "Together, these resources can be combined with any generative LLM API to power a complete long-form scientific QA application.",
    "Our production system currently uses Anthropic's Claude 3.7 (Anthropic, 2024)."
  ]
}